p4grove

Intro:
A simple perforce trigger that posts depot commit notifications to channels
in the grove.io irc network. Python is required.

Usage:
Create a perforce trigger, pointing it to the provided script and pass in 
the required arguments. 

Example:
The following is an example of a Perforce trigger that uses

	Triggers:
		groveChangePost change-commit //... "python /p4_triggers/OnCommit-PostIRCGrove.py %change% %serverport% guest-service"

The arguments are the changelist number, the perforce server (server:port)
and the user name to run the perforce command as. The user must have at 
least 'review' permissions.
